            <p ana="pr12526">
<space/><seg type="sidehead"><seg type="i"><rs type="pers" ana="n_10305" ref="#fk__p_51874">Publikum</rs>.</seg></seg> ‚<rs type="paper" ana="werk_3923">Neue Freie Presse</rs>‘ <date>1. October</date>: »‚<rs type="title"><choice><sic>An der schönen<lb/>
blauen Donau</sic><corr>An der blauen Donau</corr></choice></rs>‘, wohl eines der <seg type="spc">schwächsten</seg> Werke <rs type="pers" ana="n_10306" ref="#fk__p_50746">Bergs</rs> <seg type="symbol" subtype="4dots"/>« —<lb/>
‚<rs type="paper" ana="werk_3924">Wiener Abendpost</rs>‘, <date>1. October</date>: »‚<rs type="title"><choice><sic>An der schönen blauen Donau</sic><corr>An der blauen Donau</corr></choice></rs>‘, <seg type="symbol" subtype="3dots"/><lb/>
